    content:
      "# [Spike] Unable to receive lightning payments\n\n## Description\nAmong other issues, we had to stop all incoming payments because the associated on-chain fees we were paying to complete them were too high.\n\nUse this macro when users report they can't receive a Lightning payment during a period when we shut down receive in LN. Follow the #product_alerts Slack channel for an updated status.\n\nReplace the XXXX placeholder with a clear explanation of the spike causes, including a link to an external article (maybe from Cointelegraph). It may be a good idea to update the macro with this information for each spike.\n\n## Add Tags\nn232\nspike\nreceive_lightning\n\n## Difficulty Level\nHard\n\n## Gitmind tree branch\nProblems > Transactions > IN > Lightning\nProblems > Outage > BRC-20 spike\n\n## Body\nHello there,\n\nThanks for getting in touch. We're sorry to hear you had some issues receiving Lightning payments.\n\nWe are currently experiencing some issues when users try to receive Lightning payments due to the extremely high and volatile network fees. We are working to solve this as soon as possible.\n\nWe understand that this can be frustrating, and we apologize for any inconvenience caused. Remember you can always do an on-chain transaction if you wish to.\n\nIn case you are interested, the higher congestion is caused by XXXX. \n\nUnfortunately, it's not possible to predict how this will evolve or how long it will last.\n\nKind regards,\n\n--\n\n# [Spike] Unable to receive lightning payments [ES]\n\n## Description\nAmong other issues, we had to stop all incoming payments because the associated on-chain fees we were paying to complete them were too high.\n\nUse this macro when users report they can't receive a Lightning payment during a period when we shut down receive in LN. Follow the #product_alerts Slack channel for an updated status.\n\nReplace the XXXX placeholder with a clear explanation of the spike causes, including a link to an external article (maybe from Cointelegraph). It may be a good idea to update the macro with this information for each spike.\n\n## Add Tags\nn232\nspike\nreceive_lightning\n\n## Difficulty Level\nHard\n\n## Body\nHola,\n\nGracias por contactarnos. Lamentamos que hayas tenido algunos problemas al recibir pagos via Lightning.\n\nActualmente estamos experimentando problemas cuando los usuarios intentan recibir pagos via Lightning debido a las comisiones de red extremadamente altas y volátiles. Estamos trabajando para solucionar esto lo antes posible.\n\nEntendemos que esto puede ser frustrante y te pedimos disculpas por cualquier inconveniente causado. Recuerda que siempre puedes hacer una transacción on-chain si lo deseas.\n\nEn caso de que estés interesado, la mayor congestión se debe a XXXX. \n\nDesafortunadamente, no es posible predecir cómo evolucionará esto o cuánto durará.\n\nSaludos,\n",
