    content:
      "# Lightning Nite problem\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlightning_nite\nn156\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHi there, thanks for reaching out.\n  \nWe received several cases from users having problems with Lightning Nite, in which they hadn't made the payments.  \n  \nBased on all previous cases, it is likely that Lightning Nite is unable to pay invoices generated by self-custodial wallets (such as Muun) whose end nodes are private.  \n  \nCheers,\n\n\n--\n\n# Lightning Nite problem [ES]\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlightning_nite\nn156\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHola, \n  \nRecibimos varios casos de usuarios teniendo problemas con Lightning Nite. En todos los casos que vimos, el pago no había sido realizado.\n  \nBasandome en casos previos, es probable que Lightning Nite no esté pudiendo pagar facturas generadas por billeteras de custodia propia (como es Muun) cuyos nodos finales son privados. \n  \nSaludos,\n\n\n--\n\n",
