      '# LNURL error report Satoshimillions\n\n## Description\nWhen to use this macro?\nThe ticket contains an error report generated by satoshimillions.io with the error message "Wallet busy try again soon".\n\n## Add Tags\nn191\n\n## Difficulty level\n\n## Body\nHi,\n\nThanks for sharing the error report Muun generated.\n \nlnbits.satoshimillions.io, the service that created the QR code you scanned, gives the following error: "Wallet busy try again soon".\n \nIt seems that the sender\'s service requires you to wait a little longer to withdraw your funds. The problem is on their side, and there is nothing we can do to solve it.\n \nI\'d suggest you retry in a few minutes, or get in touch with the sender and report your problem.\n \nCheers,\n\n--\n\n# LNURL error report Satoshimillions [ES]\n\n## Description\nWhen to use this macro?\nThe ticket contains an error report generated by satoshimillions.io with the error message "Wallet busy try again soon".\n\n## Add Tags\nn191\n\n## Difficulty level\n\n## Body\nHola,\n\nGracias por compartirnos el reporte de error que te mostró Muun.\n\nlnbits.satoshimillions.io, el servicio que creó el código QR que escaneaste, indica el siguiente mensaje de error: "Wallet busy try again soon" ("Monedero ocupado, reintente más tarde")\n\nParece que el servicio del remitente del pago necesita que esperes unos instantes para que retires tus fondos. El problema está del lado de ellos, y no hay nada que podamos hacer para resolverlo.\n\nTe sugiero que reintentes usar el código en unos minutos, o que te pongas en contacto con quien te envía los fondos, y le reportes tu problema.\n\nSaludos,\n',
