    path: "cx/macroszendesk/displaying_bitcoin_price.md",
    content:
      "# Displaying Bitcoin Price\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro? Is there another macro for those cases?\nThe user want to know what exchange rates we use. In that case, we have the macro n24 - Exchange Rates\n\nAn example of when not to use this macro:\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/9013\n## Add Tags\nbtc_price\nn38\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHi there,\n  \nThank you for taking the time to give us your suggestion on how to improve Muun.  \n  \nSo far, we have focused Muun's features and design mostly on payments, without too much consideration for a wallet's portfolio/investment aspect - of which the Bitcoin price is a crucial data point, for sure. \n  \nSome other users have also requested to see alerts on the price of Bitcoin, so we'll consider adding it in the future. I'll add your +1.\n  \nHave a great day!\n  \n\n\n--\n\n# Displaying Bitcoin price [ES]\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro? Is there another macro for those cases?\nThe user want to know what exchange rates we use. In that case, we have the macro n24 - Exchange Rates\n\nAn example of when not to use this macro:\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/9013\n## Add Tags\nn38\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHola,\n  \nGracias por tomarte el tiempo de sugerirnos mejoras para Muun. \n  \nHasta ahora, nos hemos enfocado en funcionalidades y diseño orientados a pagos, sin prestar mucha atención al uso como portafolio que se le puede dar a la billetera. En este caso, es cierto que visualizar el tipo de cambio y su fuente es un aspecto importante. \n  \nAlgunos usuarios también nos han pedido disponer de alertas sobre el precio del Bitcoin, y consideramos agregar esta información en el futuro. Sumamos tu +1 al pedido.\n  \nQue tengas un buen día!  \n  \n\n\n--\n\n",
