    content:
      "# Hide balance suggestion\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro?\nThe user suggests something slightly different, like keeping the balance hidden in the new_op screen when it's hidden in the main screen.\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/3028\n## Add Tags\nhide_balance\nn117\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHi there,\n  \nThank you for taking the time to give us your suggestion on how to improve Muun.  \nYou can already hide your balance by tapping on it.  \n  \nRegards,\n\n\n--\n\n# Hide balance suggestion [ES]\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro?\nThe user suggests something slightly different, like keeping the balance hidden in the new_op screen when it's hidden in the main screen.\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/3028\n## Add Tags\nhide_balance\nn117\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHola,\n  \nGracias por tomarte el tiempo para compartirnos sugerencias que mejoren Muun.\nPuedes ocultar el balance simplemente cliqueándolo con el dedo.\n  \nSaludos,\n\n\n--\n\n",
