    path: "cx/macroszendesk/lnurl_already_used_issue.md",
    content:
      '# LNURL already used issue\n\n## Description\nMessages included in this category (not exhaustive):\n"Already Redeemed"\n"You have already redeemed that LNURL"\n"Withdraw is spent"\n\nServices that have this issues (not exhaustive):\nazte.co\napp.earncarrot.com\nanarchist.money\nlegend.lnbits.com\n\n## Add Tags\nn203\nlnurl_already_used_issue\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n\n## Body\nHi there,\n\nThanks for sharing the error report Muun generated.\n\nIt seems that the QR code you scanned has already been used by you or someone else.\n\nI suggest you try using a new QR code, and if it still doesn\'t work, contact the SERVICE support team.\n\nCheers,\n\n--\n\n# LNURL already used issue [ES]\n\n## Description\nMessages included in this category (not exhaustive):\n"Already Redeemed"\n"You have already redeemed that LNURL"\n"Withdraw is spent"\n\nServices that have this issues (not exhaustive):\nazte.co\napp.earncarrot.com\nanarchist.money\nlegend.lnbits.com\n\n## Add Tags\nn203\nlnurl_already_used_issue\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n\n## Body\nHola,\n\nGracias por compartir el reporte de error que generó Muun.\n\nParece que el código QR que escaneaste ya fue usado por vos o por alguien más.\n\nTe recomiendo que pruebes con un nuevo código QR y, si no funciona, contactar al equipo de soporte de SERVICIO.\n\nSaludos,\n',
