      '# LNURL Amount issue\n\n## Description\nMessages included in this category (not exhaustive):\n"You need to collect more sats to pay out"\n"Invoice too large :) Max balance: 4"\n\nServices that have this issues (not exhaustive):\nlnbits.satoshimillions.io\nsatoshismiles.com\nbe.smilesbitcoin.com\n\n## Add Tags\nn202\nlnulr_amount_issue\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n\n## Body\nHi there,\n\nThanks for sharing the error report Muun generated.\n\nIt seems there\'s a problem with the amount you are trying to withdraw. I\'m not sure what\'s the cause since it\'s on SERVICE\'s side.\n\nI recommend you try a different amount, and if it still doesn\'t work, contact the SERVICE support team.\n\nCheers,\n\n--\n\n# LNURL Amount issue [ES]\n\n## Description\nMessages included in this category (not exhaustive):\n"You need to collect more sats to pay out"\n"Invoice too large :) Max balance: 4"\n\nServices that have this issues (not exhaustive):\nlnbits.satoshimillions.io\nsatoshismiles.com\nbe.smilesbitcoin.com\n\n## Add Tags\nn202\nlnulr_amount_issue\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n\n## Body\nHola,\n\nGracias por compartir el reporte de error que generó Muun.\n\nParece que hay un problema con el monto que estás tratando de retirar. No estoy seguro de cuál es la causa, ya que se encuentra del lado de SERVICIO.\n\nTe recomiendo que pruebes con un monto diferente y si sigue sin funcionar, contactes al equipo de soporte de SERVICIO.\n\nSaludos,\n',
