      "# LNURL Error report\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_error_report\nn25\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHi there,\n  \nThanks for sharing this report. We'll take a look at it and see if there's anything to fix on our side.\n  \nWhat service/game were you trying to use?\n  \nRegards,\n\n\n--\n\n# LNURL Error report [ES]\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_error_report\nn25\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHola,  \n  \nGracias por compartirnos este reporte.\n  \nVamos a estudiarlo para ver si hay algún problema de nuestro lado.\n  \nQué servicio/juego estabas tratando de usar?\n  \nSaludos,\n  \n\n\n--\n\n",
