    content:
      '# LNURL pay read as LNURL withdraw\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_pay\nn96\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHi there, thanks for reaching out.  \n  \nIt seems you are trying to scan an LNURL **pay** which Muun doesn\'t support at the moment.  \n  \nMuun mistakenly reads the QR code as an LNURL **withdraw** , which we do support. We\'ll fix it.  \n  \nCheers,  \n\n\n--\n\n# LNURL pay read as LNURL withdraw [ES]\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_pay\nn96\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHola, gracias por contactarte.\n  \nParece que estás intentando escanear un pago "LNURL Pay" que Muun no admite en este momento.  \n  \nMuun lee por error el código QR como un retiro "LNURL Withdraw", que sí admitimos. Arreglaremos esto pronto.  \n  \nSaludos,\n\n\n--\n\n',
