    content:
      "# Max amounts\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro?\nThe user wants to know about minimum amounts --> n88 - Minimum amounts to send\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/9542\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/786\n## Add Tags\namount_limits\nn158\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHello, thanks for reaching out.\n  \nThere are no maximum amounts to receive, store and send Bitcoin in Muun.  \n  \nCheers,\n\n\n--\n\n# Max amounts [ES]\n\n## Description\nWhen not to use this macro?\nThe user wants to know about minimum amounts --> n88 - Minimum amounts to send\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/9542\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/786\n## Add Tags\namount_limits\nn158\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHola, gracias por escribirnos. \n  \nNo hay montos máximos para recibir, guardar y enviar Bitcoin en Muun.\n  \nSaludos,\n\n\n--\n\n",
