    path: "cx/macroszendesk/partnership_request.md",
    content:
      "# Title\nRequest for partnership\n\n## Description\nThis macro is intended for emails where companies express their interest to partner with Muun yet it's not relevant to us.\nWe won't use this macro if the company wants us to pay for sponsoship. For those cases we have the macro n124 - Request for sponsorship\n## Add Tags\nn219\npartnership_request\n\n## Difficulty Level\nLow\n\n## Gitmind tree branch\nNo CX\n\n## Body\nHi there!\n\nThank you for your interest in partnering with Muun.\n\nAt the moment, we are not considering new partnerships, but I'll keep your email handy for the future.\n\nHave a great day!\n--\n\n# Title [ES]\nRequest for partnership\n\n## Description\nThis macro is intended for emails where companies express their interest to partner with Muun yet it's not relevant to us.\nWe won't use this macro if the company wants us to pay for sponsoship. For those cases we have the macro n124 - Request for sponsorship\n\n## Add Tags\nn219\npartnership_request\n\n## Difficulty Level\nLow\n\n## Body\nHola!\n\nGracias por tu interés en asociarte con Muun.\n\nPor el momento, no estamos considerando nuevas asociaciones, pero mantendré tu correo electrónico a mano para el futuro.\n\n¡Qué tengas un lindo día!\n",
