    path: "cx/macroszendesk/support_for_rbf.md",
    content:
      "# Support for RBF\n\n## Description\nInformation about RBF and fee bumping in Muun:\nhttps://muunbtc.slack.com/archives/C0Q0H6RGT/p1646744751358029\nhttps://www.notion.so/muunwallet/Manual-Fee-Bumping-90993949c9cb4bbbbf9de1037357e083#d5c746edd77c42a192bcd573210962f2\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/648\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/6419\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/1951\n## Add Tags\nrbf\nn14\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHi there,  \n  \nThanks for your suggestion on adding support for Replace-By-Fee. It's definitely on our roadmap.  \n  \nHave a great day!\n\n\n--\n\n# Support for RBF [ES]\n\n## Description\nInformation about RBF and fee bumping in Muun:\nhttps://muunbtc.slack.com/archives/C0Q0H6RGT/p1646744751358029\nhttps://www.notion.so/muunwallet/Manual-Fee-Bumping-90993949c9cb4bbbbf9de1037357e083#d5c746edd77c42a192bcd573210962f2\n\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/648\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/6419\nhttps://muunwallet.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/1951\n## Add Tags\nrbf\nn14\n\n## Difficulty Level\n1 Entry level\n\n## Body\nHola,\n  \nGracias por tu sugerencia sobre agregar soporte para Replace-By-Fee. Definitivamente está en nuestra hoja de ruta.  \n  \nQue tengas un gran día!\n\n\n--\n\n",
