      "# Zebedee unsupported countries\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_error_report\nzebedee\nn165\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHello, thank you for sharing this report with us.\n  \nThe company that generated the code you tried to use is not supported in your country. Here is the full list of supported countries: <https://zebedee.io/countries/>.  \n  \nCheers,\n\n\n--\n\n# Zebedee unsupported countries [ES]\n\n## Description\n\n## Add Tags\nlnurl_error_report\nzebedee\nn165\n\n## Difficulty Level\n\n## Body\nHola, gracias por compartirnos este reporte.\n  \nLa empresa que generó el código que intentaste usar no tiene soporte en tu país.  Acá está la lista completa de países que soportan: <https://zebedee.io/countries/>. \n  \nSaludos,\n\n\n--\n\n",
